Milestone 2: Plan and conduct user research 

Plan and conduct user research(s) and understand their experiences and motivations 

You must research target users for each of your functionalities  

Interview users, conduct Questionaries, or choose any user method of choice to deliver your user research and record data. 

Analyze collected data and find use needs 

Upload the documents to the relevant GitHub account as mentioned below 

Present your user research plan to your supervisor and get feedback during the lab session 
